// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1896 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 6d1075ff-3782-5af3-a5bc-66c793d8df47

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:1* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
